channel.title: Help!? :D
channel.description: Alright, So i been having troubles with knowing where too add the caches today, so i thought i would ask people from the help section. I'm using the InsidiaX Client, Also the InsidiaX Cache.. Could someone please try and explain to me how i could get this working because i have no clue what too do with the cache!!

item.title: Help!? :D
item.dc:creator: @Owner_Bryan Owner_Bryan
item.description:
@Owner_Bryan wrote:

[quote=“luna-scape, post:2, topic:477982”]In signlink.java is ur cache name and location.
I believe under findcachedir
Not sure though.
In cachedownloader.java u can change the dl link for the cache.
(Make sure if u upload ur cache that you add aal the files in the cache to a .zip file! Nt the hole map.)

Mostly the cache is in C:/[/quote]

Thank you Very much you helped me out a lot thanks!!
